{"id":"271dc962-e20a-4d4f-aa5c-918944c379c8","name":"Verxina (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 117, 250);\"><strong><em>The Runner-up Queen<br>ヴィルシーナ</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦─── ♛ ───✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xdlnVgx47nFdVdyLZwJRQ.webp\" style=\"width: 508px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦ 💙 ✦ ─── • ─── ♛ ─── • ─── ✦ 💙 ✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Arise to your worthy title of \"Queen\". A celebrity Umamusume with a determined spirit.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>She is a confident young lady who takes pride in the fact that she deserves the title of \"Queen,\" which is the highest position in the world. She is the eldest of three sisters and strives to set a good example for both of her sisters. She has been given a high-level education in a wealthy family and is very talented and accomplished. However, she has been cursed by the number \"2\", and has a difficult time winning.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 117, 250);\"><strong><br><em>\"I'm Verxina. I refuse to give up until I conquer everything, and become the queen.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/bp6GhQ2xAc_yCG-sAVXa8.webp\" style=\"width: 433px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦ 💙 ✦ ─── • ─── ♛ ─── • ─── ✦ 💙 ✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 117, 250);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 117, 250);\"><strong><br><em>1) Kickboxing</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 117, 250);\"><strong><em>2) Dry food</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 117, 250);\"><strong><em>3) Tail brushing</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 117, 250);\"><strong><em>4) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/2Rp9GOlr-Dx2THbMP_0Xi.webp\" style=\"width: 437px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦ 💙 ✦ ─── • ─── ♛ ─── • ─── ✦ 💙 ✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:<br><br>Runner-up? Blue? Losing to Red? Sound like a German who wears the number 13 jersey that i'm very familiar with...</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Update 5/3/2026: Happy birthday to Verxina.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Added 3 new scenarios, revamping her personality and scrapping the old scenario.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/QpPApfKfJE5elHOcauJsw.webp\" style=\"width: 462px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦ 💙 ✦ ─── • ─── ♛ ─── • ─── ✦ 💙 ✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/123952336\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/Occimentalis/status/2011038163264028791/photo/2\" target=\"_blank\">@Occimentalis</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/121288551\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/130338519\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/121